According to the communication of gábor fodor, Minister for the environment and water, the meetings of the professionals themselves on Tuesday, however, on Wednesday, after the official opening of the Ministers, the negotiations on the system of international climate after 2012 will continue.
The experts and politicians arriving from 192 countries of the world will discuss the road map of Bali to define the efforts has done after the period of reduction of emissions defined by the Kyoto Protocol until 2012.
At present, lively discussions are carried out on this subject between the countries in the process of developing and developed countries.
The United States have also announced that, for the moment, they do not want to discuss the exact figures, but that they were Prets has to sign an agreement on the reduction, up to 2020, of gas emissions has greenhouse effect of 25 has 40% in relation to the 1990 level.
Another important subject of the conference is to see if the developed countries start, the reduction of emissions, has to provide assistance and technological to the countries which need it.
An agreement has been signed also concerning has to provide aid to the developing countries.
The assistance funds defined by the Kyoto Protocol will be managed by a board of directors composed of 16 Members probably within the framework of the global fund for the environment of the UNO (gef), announced piac benefit (market and benefit).
The six percent of Hungary
In the name of Hungary, gábor fodor, Minister for the environment and water, confirms the ambition of the EU to keep its role of flagship in total efforts have to protect the climate and to encourage the signing of the new international agreement before 2009.
The Minister has explained that the EU has started to reduce before 2020 its gas emissions has greenhouse effect of 20% compared to the level attained in 1990, regardless of the success of the signature of the "agreement of after 2012", and it was prete has cut up to 30% if the other great regions of the world and / or the developing countries were Prets also has to take on their responsibility and has adapted their capacities.
Gábor fodor has pointed out that in 1997, the signatory countries of the Kyoto Protocol had aimed at the total a reduction of 5.2% and the whole of the 15 Member States of the EU to this time has pledged on 8% less.
Hungary undertook to reduce the gas emissions has greenhouse effect of 6% compared to the level of the period between 1985 and 1987, our countries will fill his commitment, reminds us of the press release of the Ministry of the environment.
The issue is great in Bali, because the international agreement on the long-term climate policy must be put in place in the space of two years, if not the entry into force of the agreement would certainly be rejected after 2012; in this case, the commitments of reduction below the values proposed in the Kyoto Protocol would not immediately followed by a new international system of reduction of emissions which the need has been underlined in the new report by IPCC, international scientific body, which has received the Nobel Prize of the peace to tackle climate change.
The reduction of emissions would be delayed and the increase in the average temperature of the earth of more than 2 ° C could not be avoided any more which, according to the scientists, would have serious consequences and definitive.
The British army recruits on youtube
The unity of the British army communicate, on the site of distribution of video recordings carried out at the time of its operations in Iraq and Afghanistan, in the aim of making popular.
First, it is the British air force (RAF), which is a passion for youtube: the special units intervening in Afghanistan assigns the video sequences on the operations carried out against the Taliban since March 2006, has announced the BBC.
These recording, taken using miniature cameras organized on a helmet, are checked at the headquarters of the operations of the air force has to Kandahar, and they are then transferred to London or the compatriots charge on the Internet.
The political message is inevitable
The soldiers of the air force have passed 139 sequences on the net in this way and their "chain" has been looked at by more than 75 thousand people.
The Ministry of Defence British registered under the name of "defenceheadquarters" in spring 2007 and it communicates videos on operations in Iraq and Afghanistan, whereas the Ministry of the Commonwealth (Commonwealth Office) and the international forces of maintaining peace in Iraq (mnfi) also have their own channels on youtube.
Mission in Afghanistan
According to the initial objective of the air force, videos have been passed on the net to recruit. According to the Ministry of Defence, they were also has to make known to the general public the real objectives of the presence of the army abroad.
The propaganda published by the way coute virtually nothing compared to the past usual advertisements of recruitment to the television, communicated to the BBC Gordon mackenzie, consulting in defence; on the other hand, it also inevitably carries a political message since it justifies under a special form the relevance of the military operations decided by the government.
The Americans have made a game
The army is embetée because, apart from the videos composed and censured carefully, videos amateurs are passed on the site of shares that also present, for example, the death of soldiers: in the publicity films "official", a little hypocritical, the officers do not avoid talking about the losses, but they do not present the bloody side of the fighting.
Moreover, many videos were spent on the net presenting the areas of operations in Iraq and Afghanistan that were carried out on real mission, but the British army is carried away for the loading of these videos that recently.
The Americans make recruitment a little differently in using the game of America 's army free. In this game the player can put directly to the place of the soldiers in the framework of a simulation more or less real.
