The 20 August, we fetons the constitution of our State, 1 May is the work and the 1 and 2 November, we remember the members of our family and friends died.
In addition, we have two days have Easter, Pentecost and Christmas.
The days of our fetes of state, national or religious seldom falling over the weekend, according to the timetable, it has become common to reorganize the days in the case or it is that a day before or after the marked in red.
