You yourself patient without fair reason?
When you call the office and you yourself patient under the pretext of an evil of tearing because you feel badly or you have need of rest this day, think of the fact that your work, your urgent matters, your future missions must be carried out by someone other has your position.
Do not make troubles has your colleagues!
