Do not put it on account of the possible chaos in the office or your loud!
Acknowledge it if you have made a mistake, and if it has presented the disadvantages for the others, to make up for the mistake!
Ask how you could make up your fault, repairs negligence!
You feel too at home in office?
Put a jogging and is comfortable in the House, but they are not suitable for the office!
