The Czech companies will be able to obtain approximately 100 billion Crowns within the framework of business and innovation.
The transport sector will benefit from the largest part, up to 150 billion.
The transport is the most important operational and accounts for up to 22% of the financial means that Czech can obtain in the framework of these projects.
This money will be at the beginning of an increase in the budget of the national bottom of the infrastructure of transport which is going to deal with next year a sum of 90.8 billion Crowns.
