However, according to the Speaker of the Ministry of Transport Karel hanzelka, no risk penalties in tens of thousands.
The driving licence is, according to him, a document which people can decide whether they wish to have it or not.
This is not as with the identity card which, it must be valid, without exceptions.
The people do not wishing to more licences should give their driving licence.
It is enough to bring or to send to the municipality.
The driving licence issued in 1964 and 1993 will cease to be valid at the end of the year.
However, the vehicle drivers are also forced to renew gradually other types of driving licences.
The people having the documents, dating back to the years 1994 to 2000 still have three years to carry out the renewal.
The validity of the driving licence issued in the years 2001 to 2004 expires in December 2013.
According to hanzelka, it is about a matter of 2.6 million other documents.
