Cuba, the most beautiful island of the Caribbean
For the visitors, it really is an island of freedom.
All that you wait for your leave can be carried out if you make a good choice.
Beaches and white as snow, high waves or even a calm sea as a pond.
The and the inclusive all with waiters giving you on the beach a pizza, ice or cocktails.
The kitesurfing, the course and the Castor.
On the islands of the sea of caraîbes, you will not find this list only in its entirety, but enriched.
However, there is only one island on which you will find still much more and it is Cuba, the greatest and most beautiful island of the great Antilles.
At the time of the Spanish, Cuba had been the bastion of their invasion of America.
Christopher Columbus described as the most beautiful place that human eye has ever seen.
The Havana became the deposit and the place of transfer of treasures that the Spanish had stolen and that they transported in Europe.
Then came the American era.
The Nacional was established at the very beginning of the Twenties'.
It is Lucky Luciano, one of the leaders of the American mafia, who has been built, since all that was a crime in the USA (especially under the prohibition) was accepted and supported in Cuba: the drug, games of chance, prostitution.
Among its customers, there was, among others,
Winston Churchill, ava Gardner, Frank Sinatra.
