Will there be a rally of the end of the year in stock market? experts divided by the crisis.
At least five weeks of the end of the financial year, the investors already rub their hands in hoping for the arrival of the traditional rally of the end of the year.
However, this year the experts are not so certain that it is going to happen.
Banif believes that 'point of view, the month of December in stock market generally has a positive.
However, it does not agree to make the exclusively based on statistics, since that given the current context, uncertainties wait on the markets, at least in the short term ".
Although they are not supporters so that the stock market takes the momentum during the last weeks of the year, these experts point out that "the stock market feeds thanks to the existence of liquidity, disposed to invest in view of the lack of alternatives with guarantees, especially the, affected by the effect of escape to the values of quality in the long periods as well as in the short".
For that, they believe that the market will have a rather guidance, not exempt "especially because they do not know the impact of the probable fall in the rate of the EDF, given the high level of crude and the danger of the stimulation of inflationary pressures"
Javier barrio, representative of the sales of bpi in Spain, is in agreement on the fact that this is not the right moment to say that there will be a rally.
"It is not the best thing", ensures the expert.
The stock exchange index, the Spanish, has lost nearly 4% since 8 November when the index closed to 15.945,7 points.
However, not all the experts have this so negative vision.
Juan Solana, analyst of intermoney, believes that the 35 could close the year to 16,000 points with the reorganization of the portfolios and the traditional in retirement systems which occur every year during these dates.
However, the expert moderates that things will be a little different this year since it believes that the rally will take place from the second week of December, after the bridge from the party of the Constitution on 6 December).
The analyst does not consider that the volatility will affect the tendency of the market.
For its part, Federico olucha, analyst of inversis Banco, assesses that we are close to the technical levels and "it is why we could observe a development of the index which may be caused according to the news that arrive in the European Union as regards the consequences of the crisis on the credit market".
The analyst hopes that these will be positive.
The analysts are agreed to choose the values which will be the responsible for taking the towards new maximum coats.
Solana, intermoney, says that "this year the great values are returning to it".
The expert would include in the post the two big banks and some manufacturers "because when the date approaches, the electrical sector will be very expensive".
While, Federico olucha, inversis Banco ensures that increases will be at the Bank and the industrial sector.
The constructors will also be able to benefit from this rally, if they start.
"ACS for several months from positions and we hope that the other builders as ferrovial and FCC suiveront the same way", explains the expert.
The cyclical consumption will be a protagonist in the last part of the year due to the increase in sales in the season of sales of Christmas.
On the other hand, the expert believes that the technological companies will also very well, although in this case there is not a lot of representation on the Spanish market.
Five times for seven years
During the last seven years, only two occasions during the month of December has been a month.
The genuine rally of the end of the year took place in 2003, the year during which the stock markets are out of the crisis caused by the clearing of the technological bubble.
This year, during which the 35 recovered 28.17%, the month of dicembre has recorded an increase in 6,68%.
It will be necessary to see if 2007 is the fifth consecutive year of profits - for the time being the increased by 8,36% since January - and if it succeeds in computer on his rally of the end of the year.
The popular bank will open 200 offices open 12 hours on Monday to Saturday
The popular Bank has decided to renovate a large part of its offices.
In total 200 are situated banks in the commercial areas of Spain.
These branches, which will operate under the Max popular brand, represent a great change for the Bank.
As for the rest of the Spanish organisms, since this is the first group which has decided to begin to bet on the continuous opening of its agencies to 20 H 30, and to open on Saturday of 10 H to 20 H 30.
Another group which has also reiterated many times that it would like to amplify the timetables of its branches, bbva, even if it has not yet decided to take the first step.
It is on the point of concluding an agreement with the trade unions to close 75% of its agencies on Saturday instead of opening an afternoon, but not to the public.
The results of the experience of the American people will be decisive for that other organizations or not stick to this initiative, which coincides with the timetables of trade.
It is precisely this objective that research the Bank.
The autonomous customers that circulate in these areas to make their purchases in SMEs and the trade in the streets chosen to open.
The bank wants to open these 200 agencies established on the whole Spain in approximately 18 months, since it is not about the opening of new agencies but a restoration of those already existing.
For that, the organization will update the branches which it has already in the commercial zones, adapting them to the profile of the customers of the various streets.
In this way, the schedule development is accompanied by a different conception of the interior of the subsidiary and a new design, more present, with more bright colours.
The person in charge commercial bank, Ángel renovation, ensure that this does not imply any major investments, but the appointment of, since the number of employees will increase from six to eight or nine per agency.
The agencies, which will also areas so that SMEs can meet there, will sell not financial products.
A positive experience for the Group
The popular bank has already tested its initiative in three agencies in Madrid.
And the experience has been positive, as the Ángel Rivero.
The branches of the streets brave, 'donnell and Gran vía of Madrid streets are to be chosen, and with success apparement, according to Rivero.
The Bank has currently popular 2.500 branches.
And 60 others who operate under the mark of mundocredit, specialized in the case of the immigrants, also with timetables very full, which open even on Sunday and holidays.
In these agencies of popularmax they will not the model of the bbva, where some of its agencies have access to a wide range of not financial products for sale.
'We do not want to compete with our customers', notices Rivero.
For the moment, they have arrived at an agreement with Telefónica to sell mobile telephones, with an external staff to the Bank.
