The conference approves the transposition of the MiFID, which entered into force on 1 November
At the same time its Parliamentary formality, which has come to an end today with the vote of the Congress of the amendments incorporated into the plan in the Senate, the government has submitted to a public hearing the regulations which will develop the new law, with the objective of its entry into force before the year finishes.
The representatives of the various groups were in agreement to bring the effort made by the representatives and Senators to negotiate and approve the best rules capable of guaranteeing the protection of investors and to regulate the activity of organisms in detail so that the markets function effectively.
The MiFID, which changes the law of the securities market, means the modernization of the financial markets, to the point where it reinforces the protection of investor, improves the powers of the leaders of the national Commission of the securities market (cnmv) and to promote cooperation between the various leaders of the European Union.
The new regulation will make it possible to lend services financial as well to social specialized reasons as to natural or legal persons and creates a new type of financial services (esis), the societies of financial consultation (afi), which merge with the companies of values, the agencies of values and to the managers of companies portfolio.
Furthermore, it increases the number of systems for the execution of operations on the financial instruments, so that it is possible to add to the secondary market the multilateral systems of negotiation and the systems of internationalization of orders, which face competition to the current managers of stock market.
The law also makes the businesses of investment services to disclose information on the market on the key aspects of its profile of business, of exposure to risk and forms of risk management and it obliges them to keep a register of all the operations which they carry out, to facilitate the control of the part of the cnmv.
By way of the Commission of the economy of the conference, a number of modifications have been added, which one which makes clear that the debts will be regarded as a financial instrument "complex" being given its high risk for the investor, who has demonstrated with what has happened with the debt of American mortgages of high risk (holds).
Furthermore, they have benefited from the transposition of the direction has benefited to define what the duties that the graduates in economy can have 30 years after that in 1977, has been approved, the Royal Decree which defines the professional duties reserved for the economists.
For its part, the Senate has incorporated the creation of new faces in the financial sector, like that of the mediator, which will work for a firm, which does not require the approval of the cnmv and who will be able to lend its services of marketing of products and charm of new customers to different companies of investment at the same time.
The indication of prices to the consumer harmonized increases tenth five in November, up to 4.1%
This measure, which is used according to Eurostat to incorporate in the calculation of the rate of inflation in the European Union, provides an assessment on the evolution of prices in Spain during the month of November.
Its publication replies to the policy of Eurostat and the European Central Bank (ECB) in offering comparable data in time and in quality in those produced in the United States.
The advanced indicator is calculated using the same procedure as that used for the consumer price index harmonized, but by using various methods of statistics to estimate the information they are not yet at the moment of publication.
The ine has pointed out that the information that provides the advanced indicator is only indicative, because it should not necessarily coincide with the final data which will be revealed on 14 December.
