A colleague pass the information on the introduction in the penal code of the offences on the downloadings on the Internet.
A. the downloading a song would be an offence punishable by a penalty of six months to a year.
On the other hand, the flight in a store of CDs for a lower value to 400 euro, is seen only as a mistake (Article 623,1).
B. the flight in store for a value until 1,000 euro is already considered to be an offence, but the trouble is inferior to that imposed for downloading (Article 234 of the penal code).
C. if you fly a car and you return 40 hours after, the penalty is inferior to that imposed for downloading (Article 244.1).
D. It is less serious to participate in a fight that participate in the traffic of discs.
To participate in a tumultuous fight implies a penalty of three months to a year (Article 154 of the penal code) and the traffic of CDs would imply a penalty of six months to two years
(Article 270 of penal code).
E. the sexual harassment at work is considered less serious than to download a film, according to Article 184.2 of the criminal code.
F the distribution of films protected by copyright, and without the approval of the authors is punished as the distribution of pornographic material to minors (article 186).
In the end, if my colleague is right then someone goes too far.
