What assurance is it appropriate to me?
The car insurance, which covers the driver in view of possible accidents, implies an important expenditure which will depend on various factors such as age, sex, seniority of driving licence, marital status, the type of vehicle to ensure or the use that they in fact, among others.
To have a car is the principal.
There are that, escoger El Seguro automóvil adecuado are incluso Más difícil that elegir El modelo of vehículo.
And it is that, to choose the appropriate car insurance, is even more difficult than to choose the model of the vehicle.
The car insurance is an agreement between an insurance company and the insurer.
This compromise materializes by an insurance policy, which establishes that the company receives the value of bonus granted and in return it becomes responsible for the obligation to pay compensation in the event of disaster.
The premium is the price of insurance, which is established in taking account of various factors such as age, sex, seniority of driving licence, marital status, the type of vehicle to ensure or the usageque they in fact, among others.
The insurance companies establish their prices according to the statistics, so that the greater the likelihood of an accident is, the more the dimension to pay is high.
It is for this reason that the people of more than 25 years old, and women have to pay lower premiums, since the statistics show that these persones have a lower rate of disasters at their caution.
In the same way, using the census, companies have concluded that the married people tend to have fewer accidents that single drivers.
The use they make of the vehicle will influence the frequency, and therefore on the likelihood of an accident.
In increasing frequency probability increase.
They are many variables that insurers take into account at the time of the price of the premium.
It is for this, that the driver must study the situation for choosing the car insurance which adapts better to its profile.
We shall display the most significant variables here at the moment to choose one or the other type of insurance, so that this, in addition to adapt to the characteristics of the insurer, it offers a reasonable price.
The young people of less than 25 years must deal with various drawbacks at the moment to pass a contract with an assurance at an accessible price, as can be weak experience in the control and seniority of driving licences.
Although the ideal to be well assured is an assurance to any risk, others more economic options exist.
The most far-sighted drivers can opt for a comprehensive insurance with frankness, so that they acquire the covers an assurance to any risk, but in a more accessible price.
This form of convention implies that the customer pays a part of the amount of the disaster.
"the part of the amount of the disaster that the customer towards will be established according to the value of the premium, which will be more raised the amount will be weak", specifies shines Noguera, the representative in Spain of first Europa, mediator of online insurance.
Another option is the assurance to third enlarged, so that the customer ensures protection to face up to the damage caused to the third, but by for those caused on its own cars.
Furthermore, it would be covered on the flight, the fires and the loss of the vehicle.
A Council.
If you are minor 25 years to be careful and to avoid accidents as much as possible, since that will affect the premium, being able to reduce the price of insurance in the future.
An improvement is a reduction of the standard rate that the company.
On the contrary, a penalty is an increase of the standard rate.
"The allowances and the sanctions will depend on the company and the benefit of this.
If the company has been a good year it will be able to afford to increase premiums, "clarifies Noguera.
Beyond the 25 years it becomes easier for drivers in time to sign a contract with an assurance, since the rate of accidents is reduced thanks to the accumulated experience.
It is for this reason that it is preferable to choose a comprehensive insurance with frankness.
"normally young people cannot take advantage of the experience acquired in the previous after an accident, ensures the director of the European company in Spain and to add that the majority of accidents occur during the second year of control, a time past 'fear of novice'.
However, if the customer is married but has not yet children it is preferable that it negotiates an assurance to any risk, momento that its economic situation for him.
The marriages children are considered by the insurers as being the people with the lowest rate of disasters, because the increases will be weaker.
In this case the best assurance would be an assurance at all with frankness - being able to be 300 Euros), or an assurance to third enlarged from the third year of life of the vehicle when the assured has a high level of improvement.
"they have a more relaxed and they have a greater purchasing power to allow itself the luxury of accepting a quantity of frankness", judge shines Noguera.
For the pensioners an assurance at all with frankness is preferable (being this 150 euro), or a asurance with third widened when the insurer has a high level of improvement.
It must be said that the car insurance is something important, not only because it covers the driver in view of possible accidents, but also because it represents an important expenditure, it is for that that it is fundamental to study properly the assurance that suits us more according to our personal situation.
