Von beust crop criticism for the cancellation of the Olympics.
The decline of the Mayor of with the candidature of Hamburg for Summer Olympic Games ran up in politics and the economy to virulent criticisms.
Many people want to continue to fight for the Games to the edge of the water.
But von beust calls the realism in the evaluation of the chances.
The main manager of the Chamber of Commerce in Hamburg, Hans schmidt-trenz, represented on Wednesday a abandonment as being "bad for the local economy".
Recently, no other project had deployed all the forces of motivation in the city that idea.
"without this objective, the momentum would not have been able to be maintained in the same measures".
Schmidt-trenz invites the Senate not to bury the project, but to find a new point of departure in the longer term, "which takes as a point of departure another agenda".
The Mayor Ole von beust remained on Wednesday in its previous statements, according to which the Olympic ambitions of Hamburg were unrealistic at least until the year 2028.
"It is not Hamburg which decides to an application to the Olympics, but the German Federation of the Olympic sports" von beust in online Welt said.
It renvoit amounts to the decision of the Federation of sports at the beginning of December, in connection with the application of Munich for the winter games of 2018.
This priority means for us, that, in the period of time that we had expected until 2028 even there, we will have no chance. "
However the dream does not belong to the past, von beust.
The Sport Federation of Hamburg (hsb) regretted the declarations of beust.
The impression is given that Hamburg does not want to put his candidature for the Olympic Games in the next 25 years.
"It is too early to close an opportunity, burying the projects already now", said on Wednesday, the President of the hsb Günter ploß.
An abandonment of the application would be in contradiction with the statements of the leader of the Senate, on the occasion of the reception in pleinière Assembly of the German Federation of higher schools of sport.
There, the von beust would have described the candidature of Hamburg in universiades 2015 as being "not a substitute" to the Olympic Games in Hamburg.
The confederation of higher schools of sport had initially in the past weeks nominated Hamburg as candidate city.
The SPD fraction of the mayor has accused the Senate not to have used this precious time in the construction of housing in Hamburg.
"the development of small grasbrook was refused by the Senate for years because it has played the map of the Olympics and excluded the construction of housing," the delegates of the SPD Carola veit and Jan quast.
While the SPD has always asked for the small grasbrook a plan integrated in the Olympics and the use of the accommodation, the CDU would bet exclusively on the "factor".
The application for the Summer Olympic Games in 2012 for its part would have raised in Hamburg a great enthusiasm.
Hamburg was though against Leipzig.
This is not the cases of warhols.
The one which links Sweden concepts and wooden case, believe in Ikea, but not Andy warhol.
Or if?
At present, the cases in wood produced in Sweden throw shadow on the list of the works of warhol.
A large part of the ninety brillo-boxs of "Stockholm type" there are listed.
According to the Swedish newspaper "expressen" questioned some months ago the authenticity of the 1968 Andy warhol, the internal investigations of the moderna Stockholm today will lead to a result: six "brillo-boxes", which the former director of the museum Hulten gave in 1995 to the will, are copies - so that a large part of the other hundreds of "type of Stockholm", that circulate on the international market of art.
History is entangled, a disconcerting sequence of artistic and curatoric productions.
In 1964, warhol created in New York its first "brillo-boxes", of the cases in wood, which are based on the design of the boxes of soap powder "brillo".
An exhibition of its work to the will presented in 1968 - with the agreement of warhol - hundreds of cases brillo done box: these did not originate (for financial reasons) of warhol, but had been directly factory of cardboard.
It is not about works of art, but rather of their models, samples of exposure.
At the same time, warhol had given the approval in 1968, to produce a few cases in wood brillo in Sweden, which moreover was not exposed to the will.
Witnesses to the time talk today about fifteen wooden cases which at the time would have entered right in the history of the art and bid, as original of Andy wahrol allowed, with the appelation "type Stockholm".
Some of them have reached in the auctions more than 100 000 dollars.
The problem now is that the legendary manager of the museum hultén claimed, wrongly, later that approximately one hundred cases in wood had been produced and set forth in Sweden in 1968, that warhol would then have given up.
In truth, the 105 cases of hultén have been produced in Malmö in 1990, for an exhibition in St Petersburg.
At this time, warhol was already died for three years.
Lars byström, conservative as leader of the moderna will, has examined, next to the six brillo-boxes of museum, three other of private collections suedoises, both of which have been made in Stockholm in 1968: their plates were initially printed and sanded, then they applied with a brush paint white.
The copy which date back to the year 1990 reveals that, in the paint has been directly applied without layer of substance on the panels, with the help of a roll of painting - moreover it is not a matter of a paint, but a acrylic.
"these cases have not been allowed by the artist and should be removed from the list of official brillo-boxes Andy warhol", implies the director of the moderna will, Lars nittve: "if the 'Andy warhol art board' in New York did not come from another decision, the moderna will classify the six cases in its collection as copies / material of exposure."
Already in July the board of course has announced that he would investigate the "heavy charges" which will be raised in the matter of the cases of soap powder.
But since they will ring over there.
The rebel soldiers in Manila abandon
In the Philippines, the rebel soldiers leave, which were cut in a hotel in Manila, and who had requested the withdrawal of the macapagal President Gloria Arroyo.
The chief Antonio trillanes, who accused the President the corruption and the electoral fraud, told reporters in the hotel that he does not know how to respond to any bloodshed.
The soldiers faithful to power had taken attack not long before the hotel using gas.
The two dozen soldiers took off for hours in the building.
Approximately half of them were held on Wednesday in front of the courts because of an attempt at putsch missed in 2003 - among them trillanes.
It took advantage of the sitting to eclipse suddenly with approximately 30 supporters.
The military police officers, which normally had to watch, had apparently deserted in its favour and had joined the mutiny.
They are in the hotel Peninsula and demanded the withdrawal of the macapagal President Gloria Arroyo.
The loyal troops in power the area around the sizeable hotel.
The President convened an urgent meeting of the practice of security.
The national security Norberto Gonzales condemned the action of the soldiers.
"The people have enough", said trillanes.
"We call on the people to join us".
The general danilo Lim, who ordered before the unity of elite of scouts, has declared that other units of the army quickly wanted to join in the market.
The critics of the regime had called for a large demonstration against the President on Wednesday.
His government is surrounded for months by the reproaches of corruption.
The area of finance in Manila was already since 2003 the theatre of the attempt to mutiny of approximately 200 members of the army against stream.
The insurgency is nearly 24 hours after the refusal of the army to join.
Since 1986 there has already been at least seven attempts putsch against governments elected democratically in the Philippines.
United Internet becomes a main shareholder of.
Internet United secured a participation of more than 20 percent of the society of telecommunications.
The average price by action is 14,46 euro, as society communicated on Wednesday.
Only 20.05 percent of the share capital would be held.
They had previously speculated on a purchase.
The option would remain open to raise again the participation.
With this not one seeks to speed up the strengthening of the German market of dsl, announced Internet united.
Just before, assumptions had already been done on Wednesday in connection with an entry, after that the Bank has increased its participation in the operator of network of Düsseldorf of 5% to 15.1%.
The Institute of credit would hold the money for a third party, relates to the market.
The day before, united Internet had already acquired a participation of nearly 10% in the mobile telephone company drillisch.
In the framework of an increase of capital, drillisch placed in stock market 17.4 million new actions to a value of 106,4 millions of euros.
Internet United bought 5.15 million for 31.1 millions of euros.
Furthermore, the companies have opened negotiations on the subject of cooperation in the marketing of the products of dsl and mobile telephony.
"We reinforce our partnership", explained a spokesman of Internet united.
The two companies founded the joint venture MSP in order to absorb the competitor freenet.
For the moment, the two companies want to consider satisfied with their participation of ten percent to freenet, and not to make use of their right to endorse 18.49 percent additional to freenet, entrusted Internet united on Thursday.
The two companies would leave, however, all the options open, particularly to increase participation in its freenet, was learnt.
The negotiations between Internet united and freenet in connection with a strategic partnership had come to an end in mid-October.
The poker still unpredictable on freenet that lasts for months is part of the strengthening of the German market of telecommunications.
Freenet had at the end of the third quarter 2.9 million customers linked by a policy of mobile telephony and 1.27 million customers dsl and complete subscriptions.
The holding of Internet united and drillisch held up to now a direct participation in freenet of 6.01 percent.
Now it has been agreed that drillisch would bring about four additional percent.
The right to buy 18,49 percent of the society of the investment had been decided in August.
